description: The move is an attempt to stop the disease being brought across the border between the two nations.
title: Coronavirus: Italians barred from Austria to stop spread
title_page: Coronavirus: Italians barred from Austria to stop spread - BBC News
maintext: Italy's nationwide lockdown limits travel to those with "verifiable work requirements or situations of necessity". All sporting events have been suspended, and schools and universities have been shut until 3 April. Employees have been urged either to work from home or take annual leave.
